overview.en: GA_China (basic chain, application chain, cross chain) is a new type of block chain operating system in the vertical entity industry that is applied to the vertical entity industry by the new de centralization, open source, cross system, and the implementation of the intelligent contract based on the public chain.
overview.zh: GA_China (基础链、应用链、跨链）是一种新的去中心化、开源、跨系统、实现基于公链的智能合约应用于垂直实体产业的区块链底层操作系统。
